<L>For him, that he might die and pay,</L>
<L>When we the debtors were.</L>
<L>O come with we; behold the love</L>
<L>Of our redeemer high,</L>
<L>Who came from heaven to earth, and liv'd</L>
<L>A life of mi&s;ery.</L>
<L>He gave him&s;elf to death; a death</L>
