<L>He &s;uffer'd &s;hame; that we the plagues</L>
<L>Of hell might not &s;u&s;tain.</L>
<L>He came not in angelick form;</L>
<L>O<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> Kings and Princes gre<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">t</L>
<L><PB N="21" REF="019426_0019_0FABA3C79EC18900">The quality he did pa&s;s by</L>
<L>And their magn<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">fick &s;tate;</L>
