<L>O<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> poor and needy man.</L>
<L>H<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">s marvellous hum<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">lity</L>
<L>D<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters">a what mortal can?</L>
