<L>Equal in dignity!</L>
<L>Tha<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> he &s;hould conde&s;cend to take&punc;</L>
<L>The humane na<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ure low;</L>
<L>And c<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">me into this lower world</L>
<L>Without great pomp or &s;how.</L>
<L>He did not for a mother chu&s;e</L>
